[Name] Discover
[Summary] A cross-platform hardware detection system.
[License] MIT/X Consortium License
[Description] Discover is a cross-platform hardware 
detection system that uses system-dependent 
modules (selected at build time) for detecting 
the hardware on a system. It also provides 
system-independent interfaces for querying 
XML data sources about this hardware.
[Homepage] http://hackers.progeny.com/discover/
